    BudgetServiceGrpc
    public static final class BudgetServiceGrpc.BudgetServiceBlockingStub
extends io.grpc.stub.AbstractBlockingStub<BudgetServiceGrpc.BudgetServiceBlockingStub>
    A stub to allow clients to do synchronous rpc calls to service BudgetService. 
     BudgetService stores Cloud Billing budgets, which define a
 budget plan and rules to execute as we track spend against that plan.
